- `1 <= n <= 105`
- `0 <= edges.length <= 105`
- `edges[i] = [ui, vi, timei]`
- `0 <= ui, vi < n`
- `ui != vi`
- `1 <= timei <= 109`
- `1 <= k <= n`
- 不存在重复的边。

